name: RHS_ 1
description: v4w.enko - "RHS_ 1" is a variation 1 of "RATIONAL HARMONIC SCALE" artwork based on square root combinations in composition which is fragmented according to the golden ratio. The sound and visual fragments are generated in real time, composed into one square based composition. Abstract artwork is realized in black and white colors with addition gray as a link in between. The colored indication is a "time scanner".
